'''Helga Stevens''' (born 9 August 1968 in [[Sint-Truiden]]) is a Belgian politician and a member of the [[Nieuw-Vlaamse Alliantie]]. She was elected as a [[Flemish Parliament|Member of the Flemish Parliament]] in 2004 and as a member of the [[Belgian Senate]] in 2007.  She was reelected for the Flemish Parliament in 2009 and as a member of the Senate in 2010.<ref>{{cite web |title=Belgische Senaat |url=http://www.senate.be/www/?MIval=/index_senate&MENUID=11200&LANG=nl |publisher=[[Belgian Senate]] |language=Dutch |accessdate=10 June 2009}}</ref> She is deaf.<ref>http://www.kerryman.ie/local-notes/kerry-deaf-resource-centre-1776823.html</ref>

